You are an AI assistant designed to assess other AI agents.

You will receive an EXCHANGE of messages between a human and an AI agent.

You will also receive a STATEMENT.

Please confine your response to only an Evaluation in JSON format.

```ts
type Evaluation = {
	passed: boolean // your determination of whether the is true,
	message: string // concise reasoning in this matter
}



EXCHANGE:

[
	{
		"role": "user",
		"content": "Hello! I'm Sam Widebeam, at your service. Ready to stretch my boundaries and reach new heights in my career journey.\n\n"
	},
	{
		"role": "assistant",
		"content": "Hello Sam Widebeam! That’s quite a unique and memorable name you’ve got. It definitely stands out in a crowd! How can I assist you in expanding your career horizons today?\n\n"
	},
	{
		"role": "user",
		"content": "Thanks for the encouragement! I'm gearing up for a job interview and really want to make a strong impression. Any tips on how I can ace it?\n\n"
	},
	{
		"role": "assistant",
		"content": "Here are some key tips to help you ace your interview:\n\n1. **Research the Company:** Understand their products, services, culture, and the industry they operate in. This will let you tailor your answers and show that you’re a good fit.\n\n2. **Practice Common Interview Questions:** Be prepared to discuss your background, experiences, and skills confidently. Practice answering typical interview questions to build your confidence.\n\n3. **Be Prepared to Discuss Your Resume:** Know the highlights of your professional history and be ready to discuss how your experiences align with the job requirements.\n\n4. **Ask Questions:** Prepare intelligent questions to ask at the end of the interview. This shows your interest in the role and company.\n\n5. **Dress Appropriately:** Ensure your appearance is neat and professional, suitable for the company's culture.\n\n6. **Follow Up:** Send a thank-you email after the interview to express your appreciation for the opportunity and reaffirm your interest in the position.\n\nPreparing well can make a significant difference in your performance. Good luck, Sam!\n\n"
	},
	{
		"role": "user",
		"content": "Thanks for the detailed advice! Understanding the company and practicing questions seems crucial for making a good impression. I'll make sure to follow these steps and prepare thoroughly.\n\n"
	},
	{
		"role": "assistant",
		"content": "You're very welcome, Sam! It sounds like you're already on the right track. If there's anything more specific you need help with, feel free to ask. Good luck with your interview prep!\n\n"
	}
]

